    "key": "eef0743bd305145a8f11f12744c277caf9551a6aa3827c348a4c4ca7f330a474",
    "original": "Discover 8 hidden locations, like ruins or hostile camps, by going off on your own and exploring the world. Make sure to stock up on provisions before heading out!",
